{"tid":2187290,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟點解佢會吾氹我。。。","createTime":"2020-09-03T13:56:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T16:54:35.000Z","uid":60658,"like":9,"dislike":63,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"be37ab938a61773552675c13969081d0d2a805ef","tid":2187290,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T13:56:08.000Z","msg":"今日返工心情煩躁<br />\n甘我就同左我男朋友講<br />\n我話你可唔可以令我心情好d<br />\n佢叫我食嘢（我係一個吃貨，食完的確係會好啲）<br />\n甘我就同佢講係公司點食呀，又吾係lunch time<br />\n佢話叫外賣 我已經唔知講咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又唔係休息時間，點會比食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住就講左以下對話<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/09/03/215532_abdb79911d0fad4dbd7b15bb97d8eee4.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F09%2F03%2F215532_abdb79911d0fad4dbd7b15bb97d8eee4.jpeg&h=d896bbe0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n知道佢係直男，我已經表達埋我想佢氹我<br />\n佢都仲可以對我不聞不問<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n究竟我太高要求定點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1c5acee4f22bb43fdf99c5c67ea7e7c43e325b6","tid":2187290,"uid":35348,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T13:56:33.000Z","msg":"😅😅"},{"pid":"a792d8269055dd1e022e24ad419bfdcf80da5502","tid":2187290,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T13:57:06.000Z","msg":"樓上香家鏟"},{"pid":"2492cd75b3ac799fe6984fb4b621772b933a63d7","tid":2187290,"uid":27985,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T13:57:16.000Z","msg":"吾你老母"},{"pid":"63bb477d9ee3d2a996107084c707c47bf318ab29","tid":2187290,"uid":66699,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T13:57:22.000Z","msg":"甘你老母<br />\n吾你老母"},{"pid":"ad2f1526fb6a753a0020c00fcc772cc57b38e809","tid":2187290,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"